Class StaffView

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel

              • views.StaffView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class StaffView
extends View
    The staff view of the application. This view is no more no less the 'Staff management' tab of the application. Its role is exclusively to handle the writing/reading in/of the swing elements and listen for the user's actions. Note : see the staff controller for the list of the possible actions and their implementations.
    Author:
    Charles MECHERIKI
